  "text": "CENDARI workflows are grouped around three major processes: collection, indexing and enquiry (Fig.  4) [CITATION_1] ]. The DIP is essential for the data collection and indexing and integrates services to transform and process data for searching and semantic enquiries by the end users [CENTools 2016] .",
